      <t>SPA-based SAVNET is a new intra-domain source address validation (SAV) mechanism which requires exchanging and communicating SPA information among routers in an intra-domain network (see [I-D.li-savnet-source-prefix-advertisement]). This document describes a method to implement SPA-based SAVNET by using OSPF and IS-IS.</t>
